Fuck you! What's that?

735
01:02:18,310 --> 01:02:20,550
Isn't it beautiful?
Bobby brought it.

736
01:02:20,670 --> 01:02:26,390
Hey, wait. Today's Thursday and
you said I'd get an advance.

737
01:02:26,470 --> 01:02:28,550
Don't bother me now, Gringo.

738
01:02:28,670 --> 01:02:32,870
Leave him alone, Bobby.
Can't you see how he is? PoorJuan.

739
01:02:32,990 --> 01:02:34,990
Well, to cheer you up...

740
01:02:35,110 --> 01:02:39,390
I'll show you the surprise
I'm making for the President.

741
01:02:39,510 --> 01:02:41,030
Surprise!

742
01:02:47,790 --> 01:02:48,990
Do you like it?

743
01:02:50,350 --> 01:02:53,310
-It is very nice.
-Bobby helped me.

744
01:02:54,830 --> 01:02:56,870
I'm so pleased you like it, dear.

745
01:02:57,910 --> 01:03:00,910
Now I'll show you how
we dance in America.

746
01:03:49,910 --> 01:03:53,790
I'm telling you these bitches
are fucking with me.

747
01:03:53,910 --> 01:03:57,830
Don't go soft on them or
they'll do whatever they want.

748
01:03:57,910 --> 01:04:01,910
Stay in control is all I'm asking
you to do. You've seen--

749
01:04:10,870 --> 01:04:17,270
Vargas, you're not planning to
kill me too, are you? No, no.

750
01:04:17,350 --> 01:04:24,110
Please. Look, I'll give you
everything I've got. Look.

751
01:04:24,190 --> 01:04:25,990
I've got more money in the house.

752
01:04:26,110 --> 01:04:29,390
Put the gun down. You're too much
of an asshole with that gun.

753
01:04:29,510 --> 01:04:30,470
Don't kill me!

754
01:04:30,590 --> 01:04:34,830
Shhh. I've got news
for you, Doña Lupe.

755
01:04:35,870 --> 01:04:37,870
Good news and bad news.

756
01:04:39,070 --> 01:04:41,750
The good news is that those
who repent go to Heaven.

757
01:04:42,910 --> 01:04:44,870
And the bad news?

758
01:04:45,910 --> 01:04:49,150
It's your turn to
face Herod's Law.

759
01:04:55,910 --> 01:04:59,230
There, you old witch!

760
01:04:59,350 --> 01:05:02,990
That's for disrespecting me...

761
01:05:03,110 --> 01:05:06,470
...and that's for not respecting
the nation's institutions...

762
01:05:06,590 --> 01:05:10,830
...and that's for your foul mouth.

763
01:05:46,870 --> 01:05:49,870
Juan,Juan, wake up!

764
01:05:58,910 --> 01:06:02,750
What? What's the matter, honey?

765
01:06:02,830 --> 01:06:05,990
I've been trying to awake you all day,
but I couldn't.

766
01:06:06,110 --> 01:06:07,190
Where were you last night?

767
01:06:07,310 --> 01:06:13,590
Well, I couldn't sleep and
I had some business to take care of.

768
01:06:13,670 --> 01:06:16,390
Don't play dumb,Juan.
I know everything.

769
01:06:16,470 --> 01:06:18,350
What do you know?

770
01:06:18,470 --> 01:06:22,430
That you spend all day at the brothel
with Doña Lupe's whores...

771
01:06:22,550 --> 01:06:25,750
...and one day,
you'll catch a disease off them.

772
01:06:25,870 --> 01:06:27,270
Oh, my love! No way!

773
01:07:05,830 --> 01:07:10,150
Honorable Congress
of the Union...

774
01:07:10,230 --> 01:07:15,150
fellow Congressmen,
citizens and patriots.

775
01:07:16,230 --> 01:07:18,870
Thank you for this distinction
from my party.

776
01:07:22,390 --> 01:07:23,870
My party?

777
01:07:27,470 --> 01:07:28,870
My party!

778
01:07:38,870 --> 01:07:41,990
Gloria, Gloria. Have you
seen my ''PRI'' badge?

779
01:07:43,630 --> 01:07:46,030
Maybe one of your
girlfriends has it.

780
01:07:54,030 --> 01:07:56,310
-Is a son of a bitch.
-No, no. Is an...

781
01:08:23,830 --> 01:08:25,830
My party, my party.

782
01:09:04,830 --> 01:09:05,790
My badge!

783
01:09:18,830 --> 01:09:21,750
What's this, Pek?

784
01:09:21,830 --> 01:09:25,030
Some locals brought them. I
was looking for you to tell you.

785
01:09:25,150 --> 01:09:27,950
But, but they're dead, Pek!
Where did they find them?

786
01:09:28,030 --> 01:09:31,750
-In the deep creek.
-And what else? Tell me!

787
01:09:31,830 --> 01:09:35,830
They were found this morning by some
peasants who were taking their animals out.

788
01:09:35,950 --> 01:09:38,110
I think it was robbery Licenciado.

789
01:09:38,230 --> 01:09:40,110
They had nothing
of value on them.

790
01:09:40,870 --> 01:09:42,750
-That's very strange, Pek.
-Yes.

791
01:09:42,870 --> 01:09:46,790
Go and take a statement
from the peasants.

792
01:09:46,910 --> 01:09:49,830
-See if they know anything else.
-Yes, Licenciado.

793
01:09:55,750 --> 01:09:59,430
Fucking Doña Lupe!
Even in death you won't leave me alone.

794
01:10:56,350 --> 01:10:58,390
Rest in peace.

795
01:11:04,950 --> 01:11:06,510
Thank you for coming, Padre.

796
01:11:10,110 --> 01:11:12,390
Is this all the salvation
of a soul is worth to you?

797
01:11:12,470 --> 01:11:17,310
But Doña Lupe left us nothing.
Even her shoes got stolen.

798
01:11:19,670 --> 01:11:21,230
Good-bye, Licenciado.

799
01:11:26,550 --> 01:11:28,310
Don't worry, Padre.
I'll take care of it.

800
01:11:28,430 --> 01:11:32,190
Good-bye, daughters.
God bless you.

801
01:11:35,430 --> 01:11:38,750
Girls, you know how sorry I am.

802
01:11:39,590 --> 01:11:42,550
Doña Lupe was like... like...

803
01:11:43,590 --> 01:11:45,470
a sister to me.

804
01:11:45,590 --> 01:11:48,550
Always so happy, so kind.

805
01:11:49,590 --> 01:11:53,470
But death comes when
we least expect it.

806
01:11:53,590 --> 01:11:56,550
Thanks for coming, Licenciado.

807
01:11:59,270 --> 01:12:01,750
And you know you can count
on me for anything.

808
01:12:03,550 --> 01:12:08,510
Hey, listen. When do we
reopen the business, girls?

809
01:12:22,550 --> 01:12:26,510
See, Doña Lupe? Nobody knows
who they're working for.

810
01:12:31,150 --> 01:12:32,110
Afternoon.

811
01:12:36,550 --> 01:12:41,750
What's up, Licenciado? Heard anything
about the murder of Doña Lupe?

812
01:12:41,830 --> 01:12:46,190
We're on the case.
There are several suspects.

813
01:12:46,270 --> 01:12:49,470
Everything points to a crime of passion.

814
01:12:49,590 --> 01:12:52,110
Passion?
What about the robbery?

815
01:12:52,230 --> 01:12:56,470
That was a red herring.
But I didn't come to discuss that.

816
01:12:56,590 --> 01:12:57,830
I want you to do me a favor.

817
01:12:57,950 --> 01:13:00,990
But I've already paid
you for the month.

818
01:13:01,110 --> 01:13:03,550
No, no. Nothing to do with that.

819
01:13:03,670 --> 01:13:05,190
I'm here to make a business proposal.

820
01:13:06,910 --> 01:13:09,510
I've got to find a place
for Doña Lupe's girls...

821
01:13:09,590 --> 01:13:11,150
...and I thought we could
get together on this.

822
01:13:11,270 --> 01:13:15,590
No, Licenciado.
My business isn't prostitution.

823
01:13:15,710 --> 01:13:18,110
I guarantee you, we'll get loaded.
What do you say?

824
01:13:18,190 --> 01:13:19,990
No, Licenciado.

825
01:13:22,790 --> 01:13:24,230
Fine.

826
01:13:24,350 --> 01:13:25,750
Cheers.

827
01:13:31,750 --> 01:13:34,430
Look! There's my boss.

828
01:13:34,510 --> 01:13:36,390
He'll make it as governor, no?

829
01:13:36,510 --> 01:13:39,230
Well, it won't be easy for him.

830
01:13:39,310 --> 01:13:41,470
Terrazas is related to President Alemán.

831
01:13:41,590 --> 01:13:44,310
He's got the party base
behind him-- even the unions.

832
01:13:44,390 --> 01:13:47,310
My chief won't allow it.
He's a good bastard.

833
01:13:47,390 --> 01:13:51,550
If he wins,
I'll be in the big league. Cheers!

834
01:13:57,590 --> 01:14:01,030
Pek, Lady Luck is smiling on us.

835
01:14:01,110 --> 01:14:04,830
Someone did us a big favor
getting rid of Doña Lupe.

836
01:14:04,910 --> 01:14:10,550
And our boss is set to be governor now.
Nothing can stop us.

837
01:14:12,510 --> 01:14:16,470
Good afternoon, Doctor.
You must be pleased.

838
01:14:17,550 --> 01:14:21,510
You were the only person who
wanted Doña Lupe gone...

839
01:14:22,550 --> 01:14:25,990
...and now it's going to be real
hard for her to come back.

840
01:14:26,070 --> 01:14:30,390
Are you insinuating I had
something to do with this crime?

841
01:14:30,510 --> 01:14:34,070
You were the only one who
had anything against her, right?

842
01:14:34,190 --> 01:14:37,710
That's a lie! You are a
shameless opportunist!

843
01:14:37,830 --> 01:14:39,430
Don't get excited, Doctor.

844
01:14:42,710 --> 01:14:46,190
I'm sure you killed her.

845
01:14:47,190 --> 01:14:51,270
But you'll be sorry, Licenciado.

846
01:14:51,350 --> 01:14:52,950
That's it!

847
01:15:00,990 --> 01:15:04,230
Listen, Licenciado.
This isn't a good idea.

848
01:15:04,350 --> 01:15:06,270
Hardly anyone here can read.

849
01:15:06,390 --> 01:15:08,470
It doesn't matter, Pek.
It's got to work for something.

850
01:15:13,590 --> 01:15:17,510
-Doña Lupe. Fifty pesos.
-What?

851
01:15:17,630 --> 01:15:20,270
-He's asking what it says.
-Didn't I tell you?

852
01:15:21,550 --> 01:15:22,510
Come.

853
01:15:26,550 --> 01:15:30,430
Only you could suggest that
the Doctor was guilty!

854
01:15:30,550 --> 01:15:33,790
The old bastard. They're going
to fire me thanks to him...

855
01:15:33,870 --> 01:15:36,430
...just when López is about
to be made governor.

856
01:15:36,550 --> 01:15:40,310
Juan, we must do something.
Let him calm down.

857
01:15:42,030 --> 01:15:45,550
Then early tomorrow,
go and apologize.

858
01:15:45,670 --> 01:15:48,470
Humiliate yourself if you must
but calm him down.

859
01:15:49,350 --> 01:15:52,110
Who knows what the bastard's
capable of?

860
01:15:52,950 --> 01:15:57,510
Make something up.
Tell him you've found a suspect.

861
01:16:32,550 --> 01:16:34,510
Hey, girl, is your boss in?

862
01:16:36,550 --> 01:16:39,150
-Hello, Rosita.
-Hello.

863
01:16:39,270 --> 01:16:42,430
I'm sorry to be here so early
without warning...

864
01:16:42,550 --> 01:16:44,430
but I must speak with your husband.

865
01:16:44,550 --> 01:16:49,510
Chencha! Go and fetch some firewood!
Stop hanging around!

866
01:16:52,310 --> 01:16:56,350
Come in, Licenciado.
Come in, this is your house.

867
01:16:56,550 --> 01:16:57,510
Thank you.

868
01:16:59,550 --> 01:17:02,390
Please excuse my appearance, Licenciado.

869
01:17:02,510 --> 01:17:05,390
-Rosita, is your husband here?
-No. He isn't.

870
01:17:05,510 --> 01:17:07,390
Do you know where he went?

871
01:17:07,510 --> 01:17:12,470
He was very angry.
He couldn't sleep all night.

872
01:17:13,510 --> 01:17:16,470
He woke up very early
and went to the capital.

873
01:17:18,190 --> 01:17:21,590
He went to complain about you
to your bosses.

874
01:17:21,670 --> 01:17:23,790
Rosita, this was all a mistake.

875
01:17:23,870 --> 01:17:26,150
I came to tell him
we've found a suspect and...

876
01:17:26,270 --> 01:17:28,350
- No! Really?
- I have to go Rosita.

877
01:17:28,470 --> 01:17:35,110
No, no, Licenciado. Stay here.
I'll take your mind off it.

878
01:17:44,550 --> 01:17:47,510
That's fine. You can go.

879
01:17:52,510 --> 01:17:54,230
Now, what's up?

880
01:17:54,990 --> 01:17:57,350
You must help me, Padre.

881
01:17:57,470 --> 01:18:00,430
I'm about to find myself out of a job
and you carless!

882
01:18:00,510 --> 01:18:02,910
-Why?
-Fucking Dr. Morales. We had a chat.

883
01:18:03,030 --> 01:18:05,630
Now he's gone to see
my bosses to tell them who knows what.

884
01:18:05,710 --> 01:18:08,830
We must stop
him or we're fucked!

885
01:18:08,950 --> 01:18:11,470
Forgive him, Lord.

886
01:18:11,550 --> 01:18:13,950
Help me, Padre.
What are we going to do?

887
01:18:18,510 --> 01:18:20,470
J... K...

888
01:18:21,510 --> 01:18:23,390
L... M, M, M, M.

889
01:18:23,510 --> 01:18:28,470
M. Martinez...
Morales... Doctor.

890
01:18:29,510 --> 01:18:32,470
All the stuff about his wife,
but everyone knows that.

891
01:18:34,910 --> 01:18:40,030
Ah, here it is. This will fix him,
but it's going to cost you.

892
01:18:40,110 --> 01:18:41,870
What is it, Padre?

893
01:18:48,590 --> 01:18:52,630
You remember the girl
who works for them, right?

894
01:18:55,270 --> 01:18:58,230
''Not once, but many times,
at nightfall Dr. Morales...

895
01:18:58,310 --> 01:19:03,590
violently entered my room
to abuse me sexually.''

896
01:19:03,670 --> 01:19:06,710
Write down her details and sign it.
The Gringo too. As witnesses.

897
01:19:07,270 --> 01:19:10,230
Listen, Licenciado.
Isn't this a bit exaggerated?

898
01:19:10,310 --> 01:19:12,470
It wasn't exactly what the girl said.

899
01:19:13,790 --> 01:19:14,870
Isn't it true, Chencha?

900
01:19:18,390 --> 01:19:20,550
We cannot allow a degenerate
like him to go free.

901
01:19:20,670 --> 01:19:22,990
We must act decisively.

902
01:19:23,110 --> 01:19:27,430
Now I'm sure this Doctor is also involved
in the murder of Doña Lupe.

903
01:19:27,550 --> 01:19:28,790
My husband's right, Pek.

904
01:19:28,910 --> 01:19:33,350
We can't leave this poor child
with that old swine.

905
01:19:33,430 --> 01:19:38,750
I think Chencha should stay with us,Juan.
She can help me at home.

906
01:19:38,870 --> 01:19:44,470
No, no. I know who'll take care
of her better than anyone.

907
01:19:55,710 --> 01:20:00,430
I'm very sorry, Doctor, Licenciado López
won't be able to see you today.

908
01:20:00,550 --> 01:20:04,430
But I've been waiting all day.
I must speak to him.

909
01:20:04,550 --> 01:20:06,550
I have something
very important to tell him.

910
01:20:06,630 --> 01:20:11,510
I'll tell him. But if you like come back
tomorrow and maybe he'll have time.

911
01:20:18,710 --> 01:20:20,350
Fucking PAN members!

912
01:20:24,670 --> 01:20:27,550
-What does that asshole want?
-The same as usual.

913
01:20:27,630 --> 01:20:29,630
He says Vargas of San Pedro
is embezzling...

914
01:20:29,750 --> 01:20:34,150
and he's made a fortune
in that fucking village we sent him to.

915
01:20:36,710 --> 01:20:41,630
Why don't you go home?
I'll stay on guard here, Licenciado.

916
01:20:41,750 --> 01:20:45,150
No, no. I'm not moving from here.

917
01:20:45,270 --> 01:20:48,670
I don't know why, Ramírez,
but I think today's the day.

918
01:20:48,750 --> 01:20:52,230
But, Licenciado, you haven't eaten
or slept for three days.

919
01:20:52,310 --> 01:20:54,070
I think--

920
01:21:03,870 --> 01:21:04,950
Yes?

921
01:21:06,390 --> 01:21:08,790
At your orders, General.

922
01:21:13,150 --> 01:21:16,190
Are you sure? But, General...

923
01:21:19,390 --> 01:21:24,310
Yes, yes. No, don't worry.
I'm a party man.

924
01:21:24,390 --> 01:21:26,350
I know the rules.

925
01:21:28,390 --> 01:21:30,350
Thank you for calling.

926
01:21:32,390 --> 01:21:34,790
Fucking shitty party!

927
01:21:36,390 --> 01:21:37,630
What's the matter, Licenciado?

928
01:21:37,750 --> 01:21:41,150
Terrazas got the nomination
in the capital!

929
01:21:41,230 --> 01:21:44,270
We're fucked!

930
01:21:44,390 --> 01:21:48,310
Do you think Dr. Morales would live
in a shitty place like this...

931
01:21:48,430 --> 01:21:51,310
if he wasn't in trouble?

932
01:21:51,430 --> 01:21:55,310
No. Do you really believe that stuff
about the girls?

933
01:21:55,430 --> 01:21:57,390
Six girls have denounced him.

934
01:21:58,430 --> 01:22:02,270
But he seemed so decent and educated.
I never thought--

935
01:22:02,350 --> 01:22:04,990
That's the sort of hypocrites
these PAN members are!

936
01:22:05,110 --> 01:22:08,270
Forgive the intrusion, Licenciado...

937
01:22:08,390 --> 01:22:10,470
...but we've caught a suspect.

938
01:22:18,910 --> 01:22:21,350
Confess, Filemón!

939
01:22:26,990 --> 01:22:30,270
I swear on my mother,
I didn't do anything, boss!

940
01:22:30,390 --> 01:22:33,550
Somebody put those shoes on me.
I swear!

941
01:22:33,670 --> 01:22:35,350
Don't write that, Pek.

942
01:22:37,390 --> 01:22:41,310
I think you need something
to help you remember.

943
01:22:41,390 --> 01:22:45,350
Go inside and see if you
can find a bottle, Pek.

944
01:22:52,430 --> 01:22:55,390
Confess and I'll pay you well,
Filemón.

945
01:22:58,430 --> 01:23:00,270
Confess, you bastard!

946
01:23:00,350 --> 01:23:03,310
Yes, yes, yes! I did it!

947
01:23:04,350 --> 01:23:06,270
What happened, Licenciado?

948
01:23:06,350 --> 01:23:08,550
-Nothing, nothing.
-What's going on,Juan?

949
01:23:08,670 --> 01:23:13,310
Nothing, honey. Go back to bed.
Take this down: he confessed.

950
01:23:18,390 --> 01:23:22,350
On Thursday morning,
around seven o'clock...

951
01:23:25,390 --> 01:23:27,270
...Dr. Morales sent for him...

952
01:23:28,910 --> 01:23:32,470
...and offered him twenty pesos...

953
01:23:34,030 --> 01:23:37,350
...and a bottle to do a little job.

954
01:23:41,830 --> 01:23:47,510
Bastards! They want to send me
as Ambassador to Bolivia.

955
01:23:47,590 --> 01:23:49,670
Me! The party's founder!

956
01:23:49,790 --> 01:23:53,630
That's how those little Licenciados
pay me back!

957
01:23:55,390 --> 01:24:00,310
They want to cut me out,
cut themselves in and not share the pie!

958
01:24:00,430 --> 01:24:04,230
But what do we do?
We're not just going to fold our arms.

959
01:24:04,350 --> 01:24:08,270
Of course not!
We'll form a new party, López.

960
01:24:08,350 --> 01:24:15,270
The Party of the Real Revolution.
You'll see how those assholes react.

961
01:24:15,350 --> 01:24:19,550
I swear, in six years' time
I'll have their ass!

962
01:24:19,670 --> 01:24:21,870
I'll be President!

963
01:24:21,990 --> 01:24:26,350
Good, but that's a long time to wait.
What do we do now?

964
01:24:27,390 --> 01:24:29,630
Give them a scare, López.

965
01:24:29,750 --> 01:24:32,670
Deal with it the way we used to
in my day.

966
01:24:35,030 --> 01:24:40,270
Stop looking so sad, Filemón.
I know what's bothering you.

967
01:24:40,390 --> 01:24:42,350
Look what I brought.

968
01:24:44,390 --> 01:24:46,350
Oh, I didn't realize. Here.

969
01:24:54,390 --> 01:24:58,830
Boss, I swear by Holy God,
I didn't do anything.

970
01:24:58,950 --> 01:25:01,830
You know better than I do
